                              'Flecho' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Flecho' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} played on a square board where a
number of arrows are pointing in random directions and around those
arrows are various numbers. The idea is to rotate arrows so the
right amount of arrows are pointing to each number. Complete the
game in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

